        <h2 class="sidebar-title">How This Supports San Diego</h2>
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <p>
            By combining training with data-driven insights, Spark 4Change
            aims to reduce business closures and unemployment in the San Diego
            region, especially for vulnerable communities.
          </p>
          <p>
            Training modules can be tailored for local industries and delivered
            in partnership with regional organizations.
          </p>
        </div>
